                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>77 Monroe Street New York</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>Jany 16th<add>?</add> 5615</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">It may appear strange to you<lb/> to be troubled with my\n                correspondence, but there<lb/> are times in a man's life, which prompt him<lb/> to\n                do that which at other times he would not, this<lb/> is the case with me. I am ready\n                to make any<lb/> sacrifices to illicit truth. Truth is my motto<lb/> I have long had\n                reason to feel very angry<lb/> at your conduct towards me. from the very hour<lb/> I\n                set my foot on the American Shore you<lb/> openly declared yourself my\n                opponent—you<lb/> wrote and spoke against me, and you did<lb/> more you vilified and\n                maligned my public<lb/> and private character, and would if you<lb/> could have\n                injured my prospects in this free<lb/> Country—my ability and Talents as a\n                Teacher<lb/> of God's word you could not defy for in that<lb/> respect my name of\n                old stands high in the<lb/> List—and the people will judge for themselves<lb/> &amp;\n                came therefore to the conclusion that it was<lb/> in your part as well as others of\n                the Clergy<lb/> nothing else but jealousy in a literary point<lb/> of view, and to\n                crush me was the main object<lb/> of all your proceedings—but it happily failed!</p>\n            <p rend=\"The following is written in pencil at the bottom left of the page.\">1 of 2\n                20-664</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ws8jc31/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
