                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3ws8jc31/manifest/annotation/p7",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>that is if you deem me capable. I have<lb/> an extensive Hebrew library which\n                will<lb/> enable me at any time to refer to any<lb/> scarce rule or passage in Holy\n                    writ<add>?</add> you<lb/> may require, and that shall be at your<lb/> Service,\n                and in that confidence between<lb/> man and man—and I shall be ready to<lb/> assist\n                you in your Holy work by such<lb/> means to put down those who rise up to<lb/>\n                undermine our Holy Religion, and revile<lb/> the Word of God as contained in\n                    <add>מבקש האמת ודורש הטוב לכל אדם וד\"ל די לחכימא</add><lb/> and the whole\n                    <add>Hebrew</add>.</p>\n            <p>In conclusion permit me to say, that whatever<lb/> may be your determination in the\n                matter<lb/> I shall solace myself with the reflection that<lb/> I have done my duty\n                both to you and<lb/> to myself.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Wishing you success in all<lb/> you laudable undertakings</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Believe me</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours pas<add>?</add>lly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">H. A. Henry</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <add>Hebrew</add>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"The following is written in pencil at the bottom of the page.\">\n                <date>1-10-5615</date>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
